All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.EventListener, Algorithm, AlgorithmListener, Containment<FSA,​FSA,​InputSequence>
public class ModifiedSafraContainment
extends SafraContainment
Test if an NBW A is contained in another NBW B by constructing the intersection of A and the complement of B incrementally. The complement of B is based on Safra's construction.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
